text = "💡 HOW IT WORKS:

1. Look at 'GameWorldBackground'. It MUST fill the screen.
2. Select 'HUD_Container' node on the left panel.
3. Click 'Apply Mobile Safe Layout' button from the right Inspector.

Watch carefully! The Joystick, Buttons, and Health bar will perfectly shrink INWARD to escape the red danger zones (notches/taskbars). But the Green Game World will stay full screen!"
